smeggdrop
=========
A safe, public Tcl interpreter for eggdrop. 
Interpreter state is versioned with Git.

Requirements:
- eggdrop
- Tcl 8.4
- tcllib
- Ruby 1.8.6
- RubyGems and Net::SSH
- Git

Installation:
- Check out smeggdrop into your eggdrop root
- Copy smeggdrop/smeggdrop.conf.default to smeggdrop.conf and edit it
- Add this to the bottom of eggdrop.conf:
    source smeggdrop/smeggdrop.tcl
